{"tid":805470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有線新聞 再見了👋","createTime":"2018-09-04T00:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T13:00:06.000Z","uid":29269,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2648c92d4fd30fa9477b27bb1994a2b1943e3f74","tid":805470,"uid":29269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:13:49.000Z","msg":"有線寬頻抽升逾6成　將向中移動香港出售電視內容<br />\n<br />\n有線寬頻（1097）公布，向中移動（941）旗下的中移動香港出售電視內容。公司股價今早裂口高開近9%後，開市早段一度抽升逾66.29%至0.148元。截至上午9時50分，有線寬頻現升64.04%，報0.146元，成交額達1,110萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/230589/異動股-有線寬頻抽升逾6成-將向中移動香港出售電視內容\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A%2F230589%2F%E7%95%B0%E5%8B%95%E8%82%A1-%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E5%AF%AC%E9%A0%BB%E6%8A%BD%E5%8D%87%E9%80%BE6%E6%88%90-%E5%B0%87%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8B%95%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9&d=fz5i0KtlmVA4Ty3kmwqQhQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5aeacf5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/230589/異動股-有線寬頻抽升逾6成-將向中移動香港出售電視內容</a><br />\n<br />\n本身有睇開有線新聞，覺得佢地做得幾好，由其是中國組，現被中移收購了，好可惜，再見了有線新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634557425102df38de04ba7b15a6b86af765d10f","tid":805470,"uid":121146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:14:42.000Z","msg":"比錢咁多年都只係睇新聞台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73627225f07f11438c015d841bbdad8136ae0435","tid":805470,"uid":62646,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:16:36.000Z","msg":"If u cant beat them<br />\nBuy them<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d4f0852f48d9bd9c29a1ff6ed95fa1b99e321c","tid":805470,"uid":82587,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:21:18.000Z","msg":"出售內容啊=賣盤?<br />\n比佢播咁解wor...."},{"pid":"de2947514c71d8bfd1d365ce23b863148607167d","tid":805470,